A tribute to one of the greatest producers and musicians of our generation. This Detroit Tigers 2006 World Series New Era Fitted Cap pays homage and tribute to the legacy of the Donuts creator, who is resting in heaven. The two colorways mixed earth tones and bright, volt colors that harked back to ‚Äô90s outdoor gear - much like the OG "Rattan" and "Trail End Brown" colorways used across Nike's cult classic ACG line. Supreme branding ran down the left sleeve - in a straightened, all upper-case version of the brand's signature Futura typeface. The jackets also sported leopard-print linings, a recurring theme in Supreme collections (see 2012's Levi's collab and FW11's trench coat).
